text: Annushka () is a 1959 Soviet drama movie directed by Boris Barnet.Аннушка It stars Irina Skobtseva, Anastasiya Georgievskaya, and Boris Babochkin. == Actors == * Irina Skobtseva as Annushka * Anastasiya Georgievskaya as Polina Sergeyevna * Boris Babochkin as Ivan Ivanovich * Galina Tokareva as Nina * Lev Barashkov as Sasha * Eduard Martsevich as Vovka == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1959 drama movies Category:Soviet drama movies Category:Movies directed by Boris Barnet
title: Annushka (movie)
